<subSubSection pageId="13" pageNumber="54" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="13.[151,1436,1530,1836]" pageId="13" pageNumber="54">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,319,1730,1756]" pageId="13" pageNumber="54">Remarks.</emphasis>
Collected from several stations off 
<collectingRegion box="[759,929,1730,1756]" country="Brazil" name="Espirito Santo" pageId="13" pageNumber="54">Espírito Santo</collectingRegion>
and 
<collectingRegion box="[994,1172,1730,1756]" country="Brazil" name="Rio de Janeiro" pageId="13" pageNumber="54">Rio de Janeiro</collectingRegion>
, from 
<quantity box="[1255,1436,1730,1756]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.3415" metricValueMax="1.699" metricValueMin="0.984" pageId="13" pageNumber="54" unit="m" value="1341.5" valueMax="1699.0" valueMin="984.0">984 to 1699 m</quantity>
depth. Previously reported in Brazilian waters by 
<bibRefCitation author="Seret, B." box="[765,916,1770,1796]" pageId="13" pageNumber="54" pagination="281 - 286" refId="ref18286" refString="Seret, B. (1988) Captures nouvelles de Penopus microphthalmus (Vaillant, 1888), et statut de Penopus macdonaldi Goode &amp; Bean, 1896 (Pisces, Ophidiidae). Cybium, 12 (4), 281 - 286." type="journal article" year="1988">Séret (1988)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="Seret, B. &amp; Andreata, J. V." box="[981,1285,1770,1796]" pageId="13" pageNumber="54" pagination="81 - 100" refId="ref18331" refString="Seret, B. &amp; Andreata, J. V. (1992) Deep-sea fishes collected during cruise MD- 55 off Brazil. Cybium, 16 (1), 81 - 100." type="journal article" year="1992">Séret &amp; Andreata (1992)</bibRefCitation>
off 
<collectingRegion country="Brazil" name="Espirito Santo" pageId="13" pageNumber="54">Espírito Santo</collectingRegion>
, 
<quantity box="[232,380,1810,1836]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.14" metricValueMax="1.3199999999999998" metricValueMin="0.96" pageId="13" pageNumber="54" unit="m" value="1140.0" valueMax="1320.0" valueMin="960.0">960–1320 m</quantity>
depth. Erroneously named as 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Vaillant" baseAuthorityYear="1888" box="[734,1013,1811,1836]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Ophidiidae" genus="Penopus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ophidiiformes" pageId="13" pageNumber="54" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="microcephalus">
<emphasis box="[734,1013,1811,1836]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="54">Penopus microcephalus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
